This paper is primarily focused on object detection using deep neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the optimization of the network for embedded devices, which could fall under robotics (cs.RO) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of deep learning techniques for object detection and optimization of the network architecture could also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
